3.3 DUIM-Extended-Geometry Module

line-end-point

Generic function

Summary

Returns the ending point of a line.

Signature

line-end-point line => point

Arguments

line
An instance of type <line>.

Values

point
An instance of type <point>.

Library

duim-extended-geometry

Module

duim-extended-geometry

Description

Returns the ending point of line as a <point> object.

See also

line-start-point, page 88
